data.description: Check out this adorable craftsman home on the secluded part of Wellesley, located near Millwood and within walking distance of Pasadena Elementary. The home features four bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms. The main floor includes three bedrooms, including a master suite. The bathrooms have recently been remodeled with granite countertops and new tile. The kitchen offers ample cupboard space, a pantry, and includes all appliances, with the addition of a smart refrigerator. The downstairs entrance features a large mud room, family room, laundry room, and a fourth bedroom or office. Outside, the home offers a deck, new roof in 2018, play structure, RV parking, and plenty of space for entertaining. The one-car garage has also been updated with a new modern garage door and its own 220 power. Overall, this craftsman home is a must-see.
